ADDITIONAL NOTICES:

1. PySide6 LGPL Compliance:
   This software uses PySide6 under the LGPL v3 license through dynamic
   linking. Users may replace the PySide6 library without recompiling
   this software. No modifications have been made to PySide6 source code.

2. Model Downloads:
   This software may download machine learning models from Hugging Face
   and other sources. These models may have their own licenses. Users
   are responsible for complying with model licenses.

3. Cloud Services:
   When configured to use cloud speech recognition services (OpenAI,
   Google, Azure), users must comply with the respective service
   providers' terms of service and privacy policies.

